Scaling:

Horizontal:

Common form of Scaling in cloud environments


Allocation IT Resources of same type- scaling out

Releasing IT Resources of same type - scaling In


Vertical:


Cloud characteristics:

- Elasticity
- On-Demand

-Provider-pooled computing resources

-Metered service usage

-Broad Network access



Elasticity:
Rapid adding or removing of resources



Metered service usage:

Subscription free plus fee as per usage


Broad Network access:

Cloud services can be accessed from any type of device

Mobile, Laptop, any other etc.



