Abstraction:

One command is used...for connecting to windows server, Linux server etc. like that





Virtualization:

Multiple virtual machines can be installed in one physical machine...The utilization is improved by 70% .

The cost is saved.. We have softwareized the server---> most imp point



We can create a virtual pool like that.




Scaling: Suppose, offers are there in Flipkart, Amazon... that day the server will be busy...

If example 100 servers only there na..it will be tough..so, 1000 will be good
on the other day, 100 only enough...

so if we use 1000,900 will be wasted


So,that is the reason we use scaling..

Horizontal only we use mostly..

Application servers support that horizontal scaling


Database servers does not support Ig..

Vertical scaling it does??



