Chatgpt notes:


Virtualization:

Multiple OS runs on same physical machine by abstracting hardware resources

Hypervisor runs in between OS and hardware


It divides CPU,Memory,Network resources, storage

Each VM runs its own OS independently



Cloud APIs:

APIs used to connect users with the cloud APIs








